Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:24.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧吧 沉睡心底的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:30.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧 向充满希望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}无论倒下多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:36.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要再次站立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:42.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是等待 奇迹岂会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:46.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越吧 昨日懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:52.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧握住 浮于银河的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:54.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}不要屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驰骋的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:59.30,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}向着梦想之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:01.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:07.02,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘着这天马的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:12.86,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士星矢 炽热燃烧的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:18.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信决不屈服的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:26.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士星矢 决不停滞决不放弃的勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:33.76,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,0)}直指Ω 奋勇战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.33,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣&galaxy字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当世间面临邪恶之神的侵略时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便必定会出现奋起迎战的战士 圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 年轻圣斗士们崭新的传说即将展开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙在同伴的帮助下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过了由黄金圣斗士守护的十二宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于站在玛尔斯面前 与其对峙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加之背叛了父亲的伊甸也前来助阵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上地球命运的战斗愈发激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距地球被黑暗所笼罩只剩20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙与伊甸！年轻的小宇宙啊 讨伐黑暗吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你认为能打倒为父的话 就来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…玛尔斯就由我来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的第七感已经觉醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只凭这个是无法打倒我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的力量就想超越我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这种渺小的愤怒产生的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有当绝望根源于灵魂深处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到撕心裂魄的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心被几近疯癫的狂怒所支配之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这狂怒的深渊之中才会孕育出黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这种黑暗 这种狂怒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能成为真正的破坏之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是那种感觉 我也曾经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你对阿莉雅下手的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在失去必须去守护的重要生命时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所感到的那种愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在那时 我理想中的父亲也一并消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝对不会 继承你的世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个世界 不是阿莉雅所期待的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅想要保护的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我会竭尽全力来打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这逆子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 如果这是你的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要和你并肩战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去上面吧 天马座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面有阿莉雅的手杖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅的手杖？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那手杖是将地球的小宇宙引向火星的力量之源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能把那手杖拿回来 地球就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去粉碎玛尔斯的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 等着我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么要背叛我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:05:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我的儿子啊 伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已不再是你的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你 是我的敌人 玛尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果阿莉雅的手杖可以成为拯救世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何也要得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我和玛尔斯大人才能靠近阿莉雅的手杖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片刻之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片刻之后 地球的小宇宙就会开始向火星转移
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 你刚刚到底说了些什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然说我是敌人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然把自己的亲生父亲称为敌人吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然要背叛我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我的仇敌！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了你 只为你一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才决定以阿莉雅的力量创造理想的世界 可你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要破坏那个世界吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的世界 我的一切 甚至我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要将这一切都抹杀吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒…甚至悲伤 都化作了我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:08:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 这是你自找的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星永恒枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马流星拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛尔斯…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在阿莉雅的手杖前殒命吧 天马座光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星烈风暴（Rubel Sidus Storm）！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你只拥有守护星座这一个力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今整个宇宙的黑暗都会成为我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 还能站着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星陨石落（Rubel Sidus Meteor）！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 吾乃军神玛尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量超越雅典娜 支配一切之时已经到来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今再无人能够凌驾于我的小宇宙之上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到来吧 新世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经无能为力了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙织小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢 尤娜 苍摩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰 荣斗 还有大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 我并非独自前行至此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是依靠大家的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 还能站立起来吗 天马座
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓舞你战斗至此的光之碎片 我看得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 凭那借来的力量又能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马彗星拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗星拳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 这区区一丝光芒又能奈我何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来亲自一尝自己的拳如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只有一丝 光芒也是光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一缕光芒 也能照亮前方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微弱的光才会绽放出强烈的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一线光明 就能继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的希望之路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要妨碍我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不是我的儿子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻碍我创造新世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁我都不会手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这黑暗中 你们的存在本身也会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敞开心灵 用第七感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让感官更加敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星永恒枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星陨石落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷电跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星烈风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧吧 小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬冲过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等强烈的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要看不见玛尔斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的光芒指引我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这光芒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然突破了我的黑暗力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这种程度的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全及不上我的黑暗力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能在这里倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要阻止玛尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的 我们一定能打倒玛尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们心中还有希望的光芒存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有希望打倒玛尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了 在那黑暗中…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那黑暗中潜伏的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚存于玛尔斯之中的 父亲的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们还有再一次站起来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能打倒玛尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量 当然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这份力量能打倒玛尔斯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还想反抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会只有一次 天马座
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰鸣吧 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到生命的最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然主动舍弃自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会从您的身边消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿莉雅一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和姐姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为您儿子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会从您的身边消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和您失去妻子的时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对您献出真心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会在黑暗中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是您想要创造的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要创造的是你 你们生活的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妻子死去的世界不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平又安宁的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想创造的…是这样的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 天马座
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别错过这个时机！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀吧 我的小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马彗星拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的黑暗…消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的圣斗士的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于结束了玛尔斯的黑暗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的内心一直被黑暗所笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能看到光明！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我最后的力量拯救地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和阿莉雅直到最后都想要守护的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了 通往新世界的序曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机已经成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙和伊甸终于击败了玛尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却无法阻止地球的崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺回阿莉雅的手杖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙和伊甸胸怀最后的希望 前往火星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 暗之力得到增强的阿墨尔挡在了两人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 圣斗士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一线希望！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的战斗之地！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
